Document: PhysicsDirectSpaceState3DExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_physicsdirectspacestate3dextension.rst
Summary: Base class for custom 3D physics space state implementations.

Inherits: Object < Object

This class is intended to be extended to create custom physics space state implementations. It provides an interface for interacting with the physics world, allowing for advanced control over physics simulations. You can override its methods to implement custom collision detection, physics queries, and other physics-related behaviors. This is typically used in conjunction with custom physics engines or for specialized physics simulations.
